This paper discusses privacy preserving data publishing, which is a topic that falls under the database (cs.DB) and security and privacy (cs.CR) sub-categories. The paper also proposes an analytical model and algorithms, which involve machine learning and optimization techniques, respectively, making it relevant to the machine learning (cs.LG), data structures and algorithms (cs.DS), and information theory (cs.IT) sub-categories.
